result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :width="800"
  :visible="visible"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @ok="handleOk"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
  cancelText="关闭">
  
  <a-spin :spinning="confirmLoading">
    <a-form :form="form">
    
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="用户id">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'userid', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="提现金额">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'money', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="提现的独家钻">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'diamond', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="提现时间">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入提现时间" v-decorator="['createtime', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="状态（1申请中，2申请成功3申请失败）">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'status', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="1微信2银行卡">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'type', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="申请提现理由">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入申请提现理由" v-decorator="['reason', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="失败原因">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入失败原因" v-decorator="['failreason', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="申请通过时间">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入申请通过时间" v-decorator="['successtime', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="申请失败时间">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入申请失败时间" v-decorator="['failtime', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="绑定银行卡ID">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'userbankid', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="企业付款成功，返回的微信付款单号(只有提现到微信存在)">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入企业付款成功，返回的微信付款单号(只有提现到微信存在)" v-decorator="['paymentno', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>

    </a-form>
  </a-spin>
</a-modal>
